         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">Melbourne, ¶ 29 March 1887. ¶ The honorable Professor Pearson, M.A., M.L.C., ¶ Acting Chief Secretary. ¶ Sir....</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">87.03.29</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">To Charles Pearson</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">J87/3194, unit 281, VPRS 3992/P inward registered correspondence, VA 475 Chief Secretary's Department, Public Record Office, Victoria.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">Melbourne,</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">29 March 1887.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">The honorable Professor Pearson, M.A., M.L.C.,</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Acting Chief Secretary.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Sir.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I have the honor to report, that of the lithographic illustrations of Australian Acacias, approved last year,<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn0" n="1">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                           <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Approval minute not found, but M evidently asked approval in M to A. Deakin, April 1886 (in this edition as 86-04-00b), a register entry for a document not otherwise identified.</seg>
                     </p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>two decades are now ready, of which I beg to send copies herewith.<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn1" n="2">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>B87.13.04.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>As 40 more plates are now already lithographed, several other decades can soon appear. I therefore beg to submit for your favorable consideration, that the successive decades, as they appear, may be sent out, and I forward herewith a list of such institutions and recipients, to whom I would recommend the work to be given.<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn2" n="3">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>List not found.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Nearly all these send reciprocally publications of their own; the few others mentioned have either rendered important services to the Department, or are for scientific special reasons deserving of this consideration of the Government.<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn3" n="4">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>This letter was forwarded to the Premier's Office on 1 April 1887 (P87/931, VPRS 1164, vol. 6,<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Public Record Office, Victoria). It was returned on 18 April with a note from E. Thomas, Secretary to the Premier: 'Mr Gillies directs me to enquire what the<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>total cost of this work will be'.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>H. Moors, for the Under Secretary, asked the Government Printer to 'supply the information desired by the Hon. the Premier'. On 26 April the Acting Government Printer, R. Brain,<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>replied: 'Three decades have now been published. The printing and binding only of these were done here and that cost £103. The litho. drafting was executed elsewhere the cost being defrayed by Baron von Mueller. I am therefore unable to state the total cost of production, or whether the three decades complete the work.' The next day Moors asked M to be 'good enough to furnish the information required by the Hon the Premier'. See M to H. Moors, 28 April 1887.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">I have the honor to be, Sir,</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>your obedient servant</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. von Mueller,</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Gov. Botanist.</p>
         </div>
